b vesztesei egy esetleges Magyar-kormánynak </h2></a><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p _ngcontent-ng-c3048536866="" class="article-card-lead"> Az Ellenpont szerint Kijev egy kormányváltás esetén nemcsak a külügyre, hanem borítékolhatóan a magyar gazdaságra is rá tenné a kezét, aminek meglesznek a vesztesei. </p><div _ngcontent-ng-c3048536866="" class="article-card-footer"><!----><mandiner-social-interactions _ngcontent-ng-c3048536866="" _nghost-ng-c121517473=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="container"><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-left"><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-item dont-show"><img _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" src="/assets/images/icons/icon-new-mandiner-reading-time.svg" alt="Olvasási idő" class="social-icon icon-mandiner-reading-time"><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-counter">  <span _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-text">p</span></div></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-item"><img _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" src="/assets/images/icons/new-thumbs-up.svg" alt="Like" class="social-icon like disabled"><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-counter"> 3 </div></div><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-item"><img _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" src="/assets/images/icons/new-thumbs-down.svg" alt="Dislike" class="social-icon dislike disabled"><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-counter"> 1 </div></div><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-item"><img _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" src="/assets/images/icons/new-comments.svg" alt="Komment" class="social-icon comments disabled"><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-counter"> 9 </div></div><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-divider dont-show"></span></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-right"><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-item"><mandiner-social-share-modal _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" _nghost-ng-c3449636036=""><!----><img _ngcontent-ng-c3449636036="" popuptrigger="click" popupposition="below" popupoffsety="10px" src="/assets/images/icons/new-share.svg" alt="Megosztás" class="social-icon share"><!----><!----></mandiner-social-share-modal></div></div></div></mandiner-social-interactions><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></article><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></man-article-card><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c609570029="" class="content-container content-element content-type-manual-article layout-element" data-content-length="1" data-calculated-desktop-width="5.333333333333333"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><man-article-card _ngcontent-ng-c818848457="" _nghost-ng-c3048536866="" class="article-card style-ImgTagTitleLeadDateMeta"><article _ngcontent-ng-c3048536866="" class="is-manual fs-24"><!----><!----><!----><a _ngcontent-ng-c3048536866="" class="article-card-link" aria-label="Íme Európa afrikai öngólja" href="/makronom/2026/03/ime-europa-afrikai-ongolja"><!----><figure _ngcontent-ng-c3048536866="" class="article-card-figure"><!----><img _ngcontent-ng-c3048536866="" withfocuspoint="" loading="lazy" class="article-card-figure-image aspect-ratio-16:9" alt="" src="https://cdn.mandiner.hu/2026/03/OVUT2pxLPoi-eHNNjsVh94Q8ypmTavOYKyU5ipGA12o/fill/700/394/no/1/aHR0cHM6Ly9jbXNjZG4uYXBwLmNvbnRlbnQucHJpdmF0ZS9jb250ZW50L2RlN2IyMWJlMmY3ZTRlY2NiNjNjZjMzMWMzN2FiNjhm.jpg"></figure><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c3048536866="" class="article-card-title" style="font-size: 24px;"> Íme Európa afrikai öngólja </h2></a><p _ngcontent-ng-c3048536866="" class="article-card-lead"> A dekarbonizáció mára nemes célból kőkemény geogazdasági fegyverré vált. Miközben Brüsszel a kínai térnyerés elleni ideológiai harccal van elfoglalva, Afrika a valódi iparosítást választja. Ha az unió nem képes félretenni a gőgjét és Pekinggel is együttműködve üzletelni a fekete kontinensen, végleg statiszta marad a globális dél erőforrásaiért vívott harcban.  </p><div _ngcontent-ng-c3048536866="" class="article-card-footer"><!----><mandiner-social-interactions _ngcontent-ng-c3048536866="" _nghost-ng-c121517473=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="container"><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-left"><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-item dont-show"><img _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" src="/assets/images/icons/icon-new-mandiner-reading-time.svg" alt="Olvasási idő" class="social-icon icon-mandiner-reading-time"><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-counter">  <span _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-text">p</span></div></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-item"><img _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" src="/assets/images/icons/new-thumbs-up.svg" alt="Like" class="social-icon like disabled"><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-counter"> 1 </div></div><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-item"><img _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" src="/assets/images/icons/new-thumbs-down.svg" alt="Dislike" class="social-icon dislike disabled"><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-counter"> 0 </div></div><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-item"><img _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" src="/assets/images/icons/new-comments.svg" alt="Komment" class="social-icon comments disabled"><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-counter"> 2 </div></div><!----><span _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-divider dont-show"></span></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" class="social-right"><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c121517473="" cl