 in Bordeaux in reaction to Nahel s death","caption":"Bordeaux, Gironde, Nouvelle Aquitaine, 30/06/2023. A masked person is using fireworks in the direction of the police.\nBordeaux, Gironde, Nouvelle Aquitaine, le 30/06/2023. Une personne masquee est en train d utiliser un feu d artifice en direction de la police.","variantId":"41728693","photographer":"Stephane DUPRAT / Hans Lucas / Hans Lucas via AFP","fullSizeUrl":"https://cdn.mandiner.hu/2026/03/ooNHYh0N_6xe8jbhYAL958XB-24rMvugEx9-jvNMM74/fill/600/394/no/1/aHR0cHM6Ly9jbXNjZG4uYXBwLmNvbnRlbnQucHJpdmF0ZS9jb250ZW50LzUyZWI2MDZlZjk0ZTRlMzVhODRlYjRjMDgxNmRlMDE3.jpg","thumbnailUrl":"https://cdn.mandiner.hu/2026/03/NMbjv2Gf-uMGIk-4lbparWWqw3wAevOctdnos6_vfzs/fill/700/394/no/1/aHR0cHM6Ly9jbXNjZG4uYXBwLmNvbnRlbnQucHJpdmF0ZS9jb250ZW50LzUyZWI2MDZlZjk0ZTRlMzVhODRlYjRjMDgxNmRlMDE3.jpg","createdAt":"2023-07-03 11:34:16","fullSizeUrlNative":"https://cdn.mandiner.hu/2026/03/ooNHYh0N_6xe8jbhYAL958XB-24rMvugEx9-jvNMM74/fill/600/394/no/1/aHR0cHM6Ly9jbXNjZG4uYXBwLmNvbnRlbnQucHJpdmF0ZS9jb250ZW50LzUyZWI2MDZlZjk0ZTRlMzVhODRlYjRjMDgxNmRlMDE3.jpg","fullSizeUrlHugeNative":"https://cdn.mandiner.hu/2026/03/ooNHYh0N_6xe8jbhYAL958XB-24rMvugEx9-jvNMM74/fill/600/394/no/1/aHR0cHM6Ly9jbXNjZG4uYXBwLmNvbnRlbnQucHJpdmF0ZS9jb250ZW50LzUyZWI2MDZlZjk0ZTRlMzVhODRlYjRjMDgxNmRlMDE3.jpg","thumbnailUrl43":"https://cdn.mandiner.hu/2026/03/_iaOWr48u68CEK0Up3Ux4khpxqCs9KphQ8Kry7oU2yE/fill/852/639/no/1/aHR0cHM6Ly9jbXNjZG4uYXBwLmNvbnRlbnQucHJpdmF0ZS9jb250ZW50LzUyZWI2MDZlZjk0ZTRlMzVhODRlYjRjMDgxNmRlMDE3.jpg","thumbnailUrl4071":"https://cdn.mandiner.hu/2026/03/sN7SngXhtLvv5-RShGNDD6945MfLSurWtWQUNfiSYJk/fill/600/1065/no/1/aHR0cHM6Ly9jbXNjZG4uYXBwLmNvbnRlbnQucHJpdmF0ZS9jb250ZW50LzUyZWI2MDZlZjk0ZTRlMzVhODRlYjRjMDgxNmRlMDE3.jpg","thumbnailUrlHuge":"https://cdn.mandiner.hu/2026/03/gt8Adi_uddQaFPcIPbSXThcIVpDTs5gET9XAWzU8d_4/fill/1600/800/no/1/aHR0cHM6Ly9jbXNjZG4uYXBwLmNvbnRlbnQucHJpdmF0ZS9jb250ZW50LzUyZWI2MDZlZjk0ZTRlMzVhODRlYjRjMDgxNmRlMDE3.jpg","thumbnailUrlHuge16_9